    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a benchmark-tier specimen featuring the high-revving S54 inline-six engine and a tactile 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox. Engineered for the purist, this vehicle has undergone comprehensive preventative maintenance, including a professional rear subframe reinforcement and a full VANOS overhaul using Beisan Systems components. The rod bearings have been replaced with high-performance shells to ensure long-term mechanical reliability. The chassis remains exceptionally rigid, supported by a refreshed suspension featuring OEM bushings and dampers. Finished in pristine Carbon Black over Cinnamon Nappa leather, the exterior retains its factory depth and luster, while the interior touchpoints show zero signs of typical soft-touch peeling. This is a mechanically sorted, turn-key investment for a serious enthusiast seeking peak naturally aspirated performance.",
