    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b You have seriously gotta see this beauty\u2014it's honestly like it just rolled off the showroom floor! This car is in absolute mint condition, inside and out. Not a single scratch or dent to be found, and it drives like a total dream. I've taken such good care of it, and it really shows. If you're looking for perfection without the brand-new price tag, this is definitely the one for you! Come take it for a spin and see for yourself! \u2728",
      "price": 43900.0,
