    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offered is an investment-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) coupe, a definitive example of the marque\u2019s engineering pinnacle. This specimen is powered by the S54B32 3.2L inline-six, featuring a cast-iron block and a high-pressure dual-VANOS system that facilitates seamless power delivery across the entire rev range. The six individual throttle bodies remain perfectly synchronized, providing the razor-sharp throttle response characteristic of this high-strung naturally aspirated unit. Power is sent to the rear wheels via a Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission and a variable M differential lock. Mechanical integrity is paramount: the rear subframe has been reinforced with structural plates, and the rod bearings and VANOS hub have been serviced with upgraded components to exceed factory specifications. The chassis retains its original geometry, supported by refreshed bushings and dampers for peak lateral grip. With no oxidation on the undercarriage and original paint thickness verified across all panels, this M3 represents a turnkey acquisition for the serious collector.",
